{"tid":2343032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★No紅毛？】華為旗下副線品牌Honor 發表新一代 MagicBook： 預載 Win10 系統","createTime":"2020-12-27T14:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T05:35:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1cbee86bdb46aaffb7d2708ce8c370a2879d50db","tid":2343032,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"今年 11 月中，華為宣佈將旗下副線品牌 Honor 拆售，買家為由深圳市政府牽頭的財團。由於華為至今仍然受美國商務部制裁，無法向外採購零件和技術，外界對於拆售後的 Honor 能否回復到之前，繼續與外國企業經商非常關注。<br />\n<br />\n今年 11 月中，華為宣佈將旗下副線品牌 Honor 拆售，買家為由深圳市政府牽頭的財團。由於華為至今仍然受美國商務部制裁，無法向外採購零件和技術，外界對於拆售後的 Honor 能否回復到之前，繼續與外國企業經商非常關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/27/honor-microsoft-windows-10/notebook/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F27%2Fhonor-microsoft-windows-10%2Fnotebook%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdw%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=ffc3a1c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/27/honor-microsoft-windows-10/notebook/</a>"},{"pid":"26e20cda197c5ccc05d68feed0b71c2386d6beec","tid":2343032,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0360c8726f42be2acc5f560149935b5725428bb7","tid":2343032,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:59:11.000Z","msg":"左手交右手就繞過制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fa402c3738555930cc88ee87b57050bb2acc1f","tid":2343032,"uid":85524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"跟住又比美國制裁 禁止微軟